data.description: Welcome home to this completely renovated house minutes from downtown. This home has historic charm with modern day upgrades. Before entering the house, the front porch welcomes a view of the Alamodome. When you walk through the front door you are greeted with an open floor plan to include laminate floors throughout, and carpet in all bedrooms. The roof, water heater, AC unit, Granite countertops, paint, tile, and carpet are all less than two years old. All appliances and furniture can be negotiated to convey with the property! Schedule a showing for this beautiful home!!
